nodes.text: Around 1 ABY, the Rebel Alliance's Renegade Squadron, led by Col Serra, raided an Imperial weapons depot on Naboo. The depot was guarded by Captain Sarkli and his storm commandos, who retreated after coming under fire from the Renegades. The depot contained dozens of crates containing weapons and ammunition, which the Renegades looted. The only office in the building contained a safe where datafiles were stored concerning the superlaser-equipped Star Destroyer Conqueror.
